    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This motorcar has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, showing no signs of wear and performing exactly as it did the day it left the factory. From the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, every detail reflects a history of climate-controlled storage and preventative care. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than the best, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class. An investment-grade vehicle that delivers an unparalleled driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
